# Astra Instructions

This file contains instructions for using and configuring Astra, the autonomous agent system.

## Basic Usage
- Configure your agent's behavior by editing the configuration files
- Provide clear objectives for optimal agent performance
- Monitor agent activities through the logging system

## Advanced Configuration
- Customize agent strategies by modifying the prompt templates
- Adjust reasoning parameters to control decision-making processes
- Implement domain-specific knowledge to enhance agent capabilities

## Best Practices
- Start with simple, well-defined tasks
- Gradually increase complexity as you become familiar with the system
- Provide feedback to help improve agent learning 